members.member:
 @fn  void ecc_generate(uint8_t *sector)

 @brief   -------------------------------------------------
            ecc_generate - generate the P and Q ECC codes for a sector, overwriting any
            existing codes
          -------------------------------------------------.

 @param [in,out]  sector  If non-null, the sector.
Generates P and Q ECC codes for a CD-ROM sector, overwriting any existing ECC data in place.
The byte array containing the sector data (must be at least 2352 bytes per sector).
The zero-based offset within  where the sector begins.
